trans-unit.source: Item containers holds item containers that implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundItemControl> interface, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.FormView> controls.

List containers hold list containers that implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundListControl> interface, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>, or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> controls.

Indicates an item container that implements the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundItemControl"></xref> interface, such as a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView"></xref> control or a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.FormView"></xref> control.

Indicates a list container that implements the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundListControl"></xref> interface, such as a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView"></xref> control, a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref> control, or a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"></xref> control.
